None XF86AudioMute		:ExecCommand amixer set Front mute
None XF86AudioRaiseVolume	:ExecCommand amixer set Front 10%+ unmute
None XF86AudioLowerVolume	:ExecCommand amixer set Front 10%- unmute
None XF86AudioPlay		:ExecCommand audacious --play-pause
None XF86AudioStop		:ExecCommand audacious --play-pause
None XF86Back			:ExecCommand audacious --rew
None XF86Forward		:ExecCommand audacious --fwd
None XF86Mail			:ExecCommand urxvt -e mutt
None XF86WWW			:ExecCommand firefox
None XF86Search			:ExecCommand firefox
None XF86Calculator		:ExecCommand urxvt -e bc
	
Mod4 L				:ExecCommand xscreensaver-command -lock
Control Mod1 l			:ExecCommand xscreensaver-command -lock
None Print			:ExecCommand import -window root -silent "$HOME/screenshot-`date '+%d%m%y'`.png"

